Class Registry<T extends DomainObject>

java.lang.Object
com.icx.common.base.Common

com.icx.dom.domain.Registry<T>
Type Parameters:
T - type of domain object which will be registered (SqlDomainObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
SqlRegistry
public class Registry<T extends DomainObject> extends Reflection
Find and register domain classes. Only used internally.

Used by Java2Sql tool to generate SQL scripts for generating persistence database and also used during initialization of domain controller.
